Quickstrike:




Quickstrike nodded to Megatron, relieved that he would give him time off. 
Even if it was short. He earned it. Reprogram a computer, survive 
poisioning, and live through being chased. Ha, Hell Beast's group, try that.

Saluting would just feel stupid, so he left the room without saying a word.

But then, he froze. He had no quarters to sleep in. Ever since he came back 
on-line, he was busy being on the run, bugging Hell Beast's soldiers, and 
sleeping out in the wild.

"Uh, boss," he said, turning back to Megatron. "Ah ain't got no quarters. 
Got one free?"
